contentrichtext.text: '''Ettrick''' may mean: *[[Ettrick, New Zealand]], in Otago *[[Ettrick, New South Wales]], Australia, administered by [[Kyogle Council]] *[[Ettrick, Scotland]], in the Scottish Borders **[[Ettrick Water]], a river in Ettrick, Scotland *[[Ettrick Forest]], Royal forest that covered broad swathes of the Scottish Borders *[[Ettrick, Roxburgh and Berwickshire (Scottish Parliament constituency)]] *[[Ettrick and Lauderdale]], one of four local government districts in the Borders region of Scotland from 1975 to 1996 *[[Loch Ettrick]], a body of water in the Southern Uplands of Scotland *[[Ettrick, Virginia]], United States *[[Ettrick (town), Wisconsin]], United States **[[Ettrick, Wisconsin]], the village in the Wisconsin town of Ettrick *[[Ettrick, Ontario]], Canada, a community in Middlesex Centre *[[Baron Ettrick]], a title in the Peerage of the United Kingdom ==See also== *[[Ettrich (disambiguation)]] {{disambiguation}}
